CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 14, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "Pulchritude - Gloria Golden and Doris Carter...[illegible]... Pittsburghers, chat about the Holl....[illegible]... Fashion Revue which in being presented Dec. 27 at North Side Elks, by the Famous Bond Club. These two lovelies will model in Miniature Revue during intermission.  Mrs.. Catherine Green is president of the Bond Club. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Gloria Golden Grate on left, and Doris Carter modeling fur coat, standing between fluted columns
